- âœ… User registration and role-based access (Admin/User)
- ğŸ›’ Product catalog with categories and subcategories
- ğŸ§º Shopping cart and wishlist functionality
- ğŸ“¦ Order processing with tracking and status updates
- ğŸ’³ Payments and coupon discounts
- ğŸšš Shipping and return management
- â­ Product reviews and ratings
- ğŸ› ï¸ Admin actions and logs
- ğŸ“ˆ Scalable inventory system
- ğŸ”” Notifications and messaging support

 ğŸ› ï¸ Technologies Used
- **Database**: MySQL (Structured Query Language)
- **Normalization**: 3NF-compliant for minimal redundancy
- **Security**: Password hashing support (via external application layer)
- **Data Integrity**: Foreign keys, ENUMs, constraints


 ğŸ—ƒï¸ Database Structure Overview
| Table | Description |
|-------|-------------|
| `Users` | Stores user information including admins |
| `Categories`, `SubCategories` | Organizes products for easy browsing |
| `Products`, `ProductImages` | Core product listings with multimedia support |
| `Inventory` | Tracks product stock and stock movements |
| `Cart`, `CartItems` | User shopping cart system |
| `Orders`, `OrderItems` | Captures order lifecycle and contents |
| `Payments` | Records all payment transactions |
| `Shipping` | Manages courier and delivery details |
| `Reviews` | User feedback and product ratings |
| `Wishlist`, `WishlistItems` | Personal product lists |
| `Coupons`, `UserCoupons` | Promotional discounts and redemption tracking |
| `Messages`, `Notifications` | Platform communication channels |
| `AdminLogs` | Audit logs for administrator actions |
| `Returns` | Product return requests and processing |
| `Addresses` | User shipping and billing addresses |

